1. Materials

Mateirals properties can be specified using the function glMaterial.
Example:
GLfloat diff[] = {0.8, 0.2, 0.0, 1.0};
glMaterialfv( GL_FRONT, GL_DIFFUSE, diff );

The second parameter of glMaterialfv() can take the following values: 
						Sets ... reflection coefficients
GL_AMBIENT				the ambient
GL_DIFFUSE				the diffuse
GL_SPECULAR				the specular
GL_AMBIENT_AND_DIFFUSE	both the ambient and the diffuse to the same values
GL_EMISSION				the emissive color of the surface

